This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with the processing of natural language using neural networks. The paper also discusses the use of visualisation techniques and diagnostic classifiers to understand the internal dynamics of the neural networks, which suggests that it could also belong to the sub-categories of cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of recurrent neural networks, which are commonly used in computer vision tasks, indicating that it could also belong to the sub-category of cs.CV (Computer Vision).
